Global Personal Fall Arrest System Market Insights
Personal Fall Arrest System Market market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Personal Fall Arrest System Market Overview
The global Personal Fall Arrest System (PFAS) market was valued at USD 3.72 billion in 2023 and is expected to reach USD 5.10 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.4% during the forecast period. The increasing focus on worker safety, particularly in construction, manufacturing, and energy sectors, is driving this growth. Furthermore, stringent regulations related to workplace safety and a rising awareness about fall protection are contributing to the market’s expansion. The growing adoption of advanced PFAS technologies, including smart wearables and improved materials, further enhances the market’s potential.

